    "body": "Hi Simon, thanks for the issue. Our doc is lacking real explanation about that. The URL sync mechanism is implemented in a way that it will update the URL (and not creating new browser history steps) if under the threshold. Beyond the threshold it will create a new entry. It is not using throttle or debounce.\n",
